<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q35_v12" title="Q35_v12" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      La temperatura ambiental T (en °C) y la cantidad n de chirridos por minuto que emite un grillo se relacionan mediante la ecuación
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>T</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mn>10</m:mn>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mi>n</m:mi>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mi>b</m:mi>
          </m:mrow>
          <m:mn>7</m:mn>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>.
      En esta fórmula, b representa el número de chirridos por minuto a partir del cual se empieza a ajustar la temperatura.
      
      Para un grillo que emite 110 chirridos por minuto, la temperatura medida fue de 20 °C.
      
      ¿Cuál es el valor de b?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">30<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>110</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>150</m:mn><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, que es aproximadamente 21,43 °C. Ese valor es distinto de 20 °C, por lo tanto <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math> no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">40<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al reemplazar <m:math><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>110</m:mn></m:math> en la fórmula se obtiene <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>110</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. Entonces <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>110</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, y al multiplicar por 7 resulta <m:math><m:mn>70</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>110</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:math>. De ahí, <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">50<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>110</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>130</m:mn><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, que es aproximadamente 18,57 °C. Ese valor es distinto de 20 °C, por lo tanto <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math> no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">110<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>110</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>110</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>110</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:math>. Ese valor es distinto de 20 °C, por lo tanto <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>110</m:mn></m:math> no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Sustituir los datos del problema en la ecuación</strong></p>
            <p>La relación dada es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>T</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mi>n</m:mi>
                    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                    <m:mi>b</m:mi>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Como el grillo emite 110 chirridos por minuto y la temperatura medida es 20 °C, se reemplaza <m:math><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>110</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>110</m:mn>
                    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                    <m:mi>b</m:mi>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Aislar la fracción</strong></p>
            <p>Restamos 10 en ambos lados:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>110</m:mn>
                    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                    <m:mi>b</m:mi>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>110</m:mn>
                    <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                    <m:mi>b</m:mi>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Eliminar el denominador</strong></p>
            <p>Multiplicamos ambos lados por 7:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>110</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mi>b</m:mi>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>70</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>110</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mi>b</m:mi>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Despejar b</strong></p>
            <p>Restamos 110 en ambos lados:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>70</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>110</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mi>b</m:mi>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>40</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mi>b</m:mi>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Multiplicamos ambos lados por <m:math><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mi>b</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>40</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El valor de <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:math> es 40, por lo tanto la alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>